     * foreach(k, v ; arr)
     * {
     *     archive.archiveAssociativeArrayValue(to!(string)(i), {
     *         // archive the value
     *     });
     *
     *     i++;
     * }
     * ---
     *
     * The foreach statement in the above example would most likely be executed in the
